HOSPITAL LIEN
Notice is hereby giveh that a hospital known as DELL CHILDRENS MEDICAL CENTER located at 4900 MUELLER BLVD,
AUSTIN, TX 78723 claims a lien, in accordance to Chapter 55 of the Texas Property Code, for the treatment, care and
maintenance of the following injured individual:
YAHIR R. REYES-RANGEL (8080309547)
11900 SUNBONNET CV. AUSTIN, TX 78719-9712
On or about 11/14/2021, the individual allegedly sustained personal injuries and sought treatment for said injuries
within seventy-two (72) hours as a result of the accident. Treatment, care and maintenance was provided DELL
CHILDRENS MEDICAL CENTER for a period of no longer than one hundred days, and the amount due is based upon
charges that are reasonable and at a regular rate for such services. The name(s) of the person(s), if known, alleged
to be liable for the damages arising from said injury are:
This lien will attach to any cause of action or chaim the injured individual may have against another person for the
individual's injuries; and the lien does not attach to real property owned by the injured individual.
Dated: 2/11 /2022
